{
  "stem": "22979.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't tell them-- the Germans-- where the clothing come from.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you have no idea what people brought along-- brought jewelry, furs, the best from the best.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But because when you go somewhere, sure, you take the best, either of selling or to trading for food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know how it went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then end of August, Auschwitz women's camp, with the 10 barracks-- and people were living outside, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was so crowded you had to step over people who were sitting outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Relocated us-- we marched from Auschwitz to a new camp, to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Birkenau was five kilometers from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We thought that Auschwitz was hell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know what Birkenau is waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We came in to Birkenau in the summer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Winter was bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Summer was worse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was so hot in summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Our heads, shaved heads-- blisters everywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The feet swollen-- full of-- of blisters on the feet, and-- and you know, cuts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because you know, the shoes we didn't have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The hunger, Muselmann there, you know, just dragging our bodies-- not me, because I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I could steal food from the luggage, from the-- from the packages, what they brung along-- and brought-- under the roof.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had water there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I am talking generally.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's not mine what went through, but we lived in the same place with the rest of the population, the same barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So naturally, we sort everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they called our commander the elite commander, because we looked fat and pretty clean, yes?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could steal everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we stole in the morning when we went to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We put on five underwears.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came to-- to-- the camp, and we gave it to another girl, or whoever came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we exchanged, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
